>> +
>> +- It is lesser or equal to the latency we tolerate when the mitigation
> 
> s/lesser/less than/
> 
>> +  begins. It is platform dependent and will depend on the user
>> +  experience, reactivity vs performance trade off we want. This value
>> +  should be specified.
>> +
